1380
01:28:19,995 --> 01:28:22,990
Tell me all your fantasies tonight

1381
01:28:23,167 --> 01:28:24,760
And I will make them happen 'cause

1382
01:28:24,937 --> 01:28:29,470
I'm not satisfied if I don't get

1383
01:28:29,648 --> 01:28:32,016
My Buddha's delight

